
# Magic the Gathering Card Viewer

## Overview
A web application for searching and browsing Magic: The Gathering cards using the Scryfall API.

## Features
- Search cards by name, type, colors, and mana cost
- Filter by game format (Standard, Commander, etc.)
- View card details and pricing information
- Commander color identity filtering

## Technologies
- HTML/CSS
- JavaScript/jQuery
- PHP
- [Scryfall API](https://scryfall.com/docs/api)

## Pages
- **Cards**: Main search interface
- **About**: Information on data sources
- **Stats**: Statistical analysis (planned)

